      "page": 2,
      "title": "Get Your Own Free Cell Phone Now!",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Get Your Own Free Cell Phone Now!</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>1. What Free Cell Phone Programs Are Available?</h4>\n<img alt=\"Get Your Own Free Cell Phone Now!_2\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/get-your-own-free-cell-phone-now/get-your-own-free-cell-phone-now_2.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/get-your-own-free-cell-phone-now/get-your-own-free-cell-phone-now_2.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/get-your-own-free-cell-phone-now/get-your-own-free-cell-phone-now_2.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/get-your-own-free-cell-phone-now/get-your-own-free-cell-phone-now_2.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>There are several free cell phone programs available in the United States, the most prominent of which are the Lifeline program and the Affordable Connectivity Program (ACP). Lifeline is a federal program that offers free or low-cost phones and phone service to low-income households, while the ACP provides discount Internet services and devices to those in need.</p>\n</img></div>"
    },
